1/4/2017
- review some basic tags in HTML.
  Text
    Structure markup
    - headings <p> <sub> <sup> <br/> <hr/> <b> <i>
    Semantic markup //to describe the content of page, not to change the look of page
    - <em> <abbr> <ins> <del> <s> <address> <blockquote> <q> <dfn>

  List
    unordered list // with bullet point
    - <ul> <li>
    ordered list // using number
    - <ol> <li>
    definition list //define something
    - <dl> <dt> <dd>

  Table
    <table>
    <th scope = "">
    <tr>
    <td colspan = "", rowspan="">
    <thead> <tbody> <tfoot> //for long table

  Link
    Link to another website; absolute path
    Link to another page on the same website; relative path
    Link to a specific part of the same page; id
    Link to a specific part of another page; id followed by path
    <a href="">
    <a href="mailto:truelj@hotmail.com">

  Image
    bitmap format image
      format: jpeg, gif, png //jpeg for photograph; gif for flat colored illustration
      use image dimension in terms of pixels
      image resolution doesn't matter on screen
    vector format image
      format: SVG //scalable vector graphics
      advantages: increase the dimension of image won't affect the image quality

    <img
      src ="" alt="" title=""
      width="" height="" align="" //using CSS
    />
    <figure>
      <img />
      <figcaption> add a description to the image</figcaption>
    </figure>

  Form
    <form action="url" method="" id="">
    Form controls
      Text
        text field
          <input type="text" name="" size="" maxlength="" placeholder=""/>
        password
          <input type="password" name="password" size="" maxlength=""/>
        text area
          <textarea name="textarea" cols="" rows="" placeholder=""> ... </textarea>

      Choose
        Radio
        <input type="radio" name="" value="" checked="checked" />
        check box
        <input type="checkbox" name="" value="" checked="checked" multiple="multiple"/>
        select
        <select name="">
          <option value="" selected="selected"> value </option>
          ...
        </select>

      Submit
        text submit button
        <input type="submit" value="" />
        image submit button
        <input type="image" src="" alt="" width="" height=""/>
        button
        <button>...</button>

      upload file
        <input type="file" name="" />

      hidden
        <input type="hidden" name="" value=""/>

  Grouping field set
    <fieldset>
      <legend></legend>
      ...
    </fieldset>
    
  HTML5 form controls
    input validation
    <input required="">
    date
    <input type="date"/>
    search
    <input type="search" name="search"/>
    email
    <input type="email" name="email"/>
    url
    <input type="url" name="website" />
